<section class="why" id="why">
  <div class="why-inner">
    <div class="why-sticky">
      <div class="section-label">Why Choose Us</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">The<br/>Difference<br/>Is in<br/>the Details</h2>
      <p class="section-sub" style="margin-top:16px;">
        There's no shortage of electricians. There's a shortage of ones who show up on time, communicate clearly, and finish clean. That's us.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-grid">
      <div class="why-card fade-up">
        <div class="why-card-num">01</div>
        <div class="why-card-title">On-Time, Every Time</div>
        <p class="why-card-text">We respect your schedule. If we're running late, you'll hear from us before you have to call us.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card fade-up">
        <div class="why-card-num">02</div>
        <div class="why-card-title">Code Compliant</div>
        <p class="why-card-text">Every job is done to current NEC and PA state code. We pull permits and pass inspections — no shortcuts.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card fade-up">
        <div class="why-card-num">03</div>
        <div class="why-card-title">Upfront Pricing</div>
        <p class="why-card-text">You'll know the price before we start. No surprise invoices, no upsells mid-job.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card fade-up">
        <div class="why-card-num">04</div>
        <div class="why-card-title">Bilingual Team</div>
        <p class="why-card-text">We communicate in both English and Spanish so nothing gets lost in translation.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card fade-up">
        <div class="why-card-num">05</div>
        <div class="why-card-title">GC-Ready Crew</div>
        <p class="why-card-text">We know how to work in a coordinated job site — sequencing, communication, and clean rough-ins that pass every time.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card fade-up">
        <div class="why-card-num">06</div>
        <div class="why-card-title">Local &amp; Accountable</div>
        <p class="why-card-text">We live here too. Our reputation in Chester County is built one job at a time — and we intend to keep it.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
